CatDescriptText: Cutline of images published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 12, 1955, reads: "HEY, DADDY! - Little Cheryl Ann Harris, Daughter of Mr. and Mrs. Charles (Teenie) Harris, opens her cute little mouth the minute daddy appears. Naturally this is a Harris photo. The Courier welcomes pictures of babies for this, the Baby Corner.
TitMainTitle: Cheryl Ann Harris, daughter of Charles "Teenie" Harris, wearing light colored one piece outfit, lying on light colored pillow, on jacquard armchair, in Charles "Teenie" Harris' home at 7604 Mulford Street
